        "description": "How does it feel to experience workplace bias? If you don’t live it, it’s hard to fully comprehend. To combat bias in ourselves and our communities, we need more than just an intellectual awareness of how others experience the world. The key to real change lies in emotional understanding through empathy. \n\nPerspectives on Bias fosters that empathy through immersive video, letting you feel the impact of bias in the workplace. In the full experience, you explore avenues to combat bias when you see it in the real world. \n\nAre you willing to step out of your comfort zone? To step up and make a difference? \n\nNOTE: This experience is a free demo. To learn more about using a complete Perspectives on Bias experience in your workplace, visit ampcreative.com/perspectives. ",
